<Content_wSideColumn ID="x28932" Name="Workshops" Layout="byuidefault.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Workshops</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Information about the Career Preparation Workshops.</Abstract><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="SideColumn" label="L/R Column" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><MoveLeft type="boolean" label="Toggle column right or left (right is default)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</MoveLeft><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ImageComponent" label="Image Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="LeftColumnImageComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="TextComponent" label="Text Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="ColumnTextComponent"/><fbookTop type="boolean" label="Put facebook at top of page" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</fbookTop><fbookStatus type="string" label="Facebook ID#" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookStatus><fbookToken type="string" label="Access_Token" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookToken><fbookDisplayed type="string" label="Number of facebook messages to display" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">1</fbookDisplayed></xPower><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>The Career Workshop Series is a series of 6 workshops designed to help you achieve your career goals. The workshops are taught on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Saturdays throughout the semester. <br />Get a <strong><a href="Documents/advising/advising/Forms/Career Workshop Series Spring 2014 Schedule .pdf" title="Career Workshop Series Schedule">schedule</a>&nbsp;</strong>of the workshops.</p>
<ol style="margin-top: 20px;">
<li>
<h3 style="margin-bottom: -8px;"><strong>Discovering your future career</strong></h3>
Identifying your strengths, goals and resources and writing power statements and "Me in 30 Seconds" statements. <a href="Documents/advising/careerservices/Career Workshops 1 Discovering Your Future Career Handout.docx" title="Discovering Your Future Career Study Packet">Get the workshop study packet.<br /><br /></a><strong></strong></li>
<li>
<h3 style="margin-bottom: -8px;"><strong>Preparing for and competing in the Job Market</strong></h3>
Understanding academic preparation, identifying the technical and soft skills (including etiquette and online presence) necessary to present a professional image.&nbsp;<a href="Documents/advising/careerservices/Career Workshops 2 Preparing for the Job Market Handouts.docx" title="Preparing for the Job Market Study Packet">Get the workshop study packet.<br /><br /></a> <strong></strong></li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
<h3 style="margin-bottom: -8px;"><strong>Writing Resumes, Cover Letters &amp; other Professional Documents</strong></h3>
Communicating your value to employers, experience providers, and graduate schools through stellar documents, writing effective bullets.&nbsp;<a href="Documents/advising/careerservices/Career Workshops 3 Writing Resumes and Cover Letters.docx" title="Writing Resumes and Cover Letters Study Packet">Get the workshop study packet.<br /><br /></a> <strong></strong>
<script src="https://cdnapisec.kaltura.com/p/1157612/sp/115761200/embedIframeJs/uiconf_id/16585652/partner_id/1157612?autoembed=true&amp;entry_id=0_zj22cisz&amp;playerId=kaltura_player_1404743670&amp;cache_st=1404743670&amp; width=480&amp;height=270" type="text/javascript"></script>
</li>
<li>
<h3 style="margin-bottom: -8px;"><strong>Networking &amp; other Job Search strategies</strong></h3>
Identify effective job search skills and techniques, expanding and using your network, improving "Me in 30 Seconds" statements.&nbsp;<a href="Documents/advising/careerservices/Career Workshops 4 Networking and Other Job Search Handout.docx" title="Networking and Other Job Search Strategies Study Packet">Get the workshop study packet.<br /><br /></a> <strong></strong></li>
<li>
<h3 style="margin-bottom: -8px;"><strong>Interviewing &amp; Accepting the Job Offer</strong></h3>
Mastering typical interview questions by using power statements, "Me in 30 Seconds" statements and STAR stories, dressing for credibility, accepting &amp; negotiating an offer.&nbsp;<a href="Documents/advising/careerservices/Career Workshops 5 Interviewing and Accepting the Job Offer Handout.docx" title="Interviewing and Accepting the Job Offer Study Packet">Get the workshop study packet.<br /><br /></a> <strong></strong></li>
<li>
<h3 style="margin-bottom: -8px;"><strong>Succeeding in your Internship, Graduate School &amp; Career</strong></h3>
Pursuing opportunities, working well &amp; building relationships, understanding key resources, planning for ongoing professional development.&nbsp;<a href="Documents/advising/careerservices/Career Workshops 6 Succeeding in your Internship and Career Handout.docx" title="Succeding in your Internship, Grad School and Career Study Packet">Get the workshop study packet.</a></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size: 14.190000000000001pt; line-height: 1.2em; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;">Registration</span></p>
